gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 116, Rockets 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Rockets, 116-107. Kristaps Porzingis recorded 32 points (6-11 3PM), six rebounds, and five blocks for the Celtics, with Jaylen Brown adding 13 points, 11 rebounds, and a season-high 10 assists in the victory. Alperen Sengun tallied 24 points, 12 rebounds, and 10 assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 33-10, while the Rockets fall to 20-22.
